Control                                            Vs                               Flexibility
- track and report on open positions
- conrol, freeze open positions for hiring process
- track position history
- initiate recquistions
- pass position details to/from recruitment system
- define restrictions at the level of individual positions
- refine qualifications in addition to any defined on the job profile
- move unfilled positions between supervisory orgs
- move workers/filled positions between supervisory orgs
- tie requisition fulfillment back to specific positions
- have the ability to have two workers share a position temporarily
